<pre>!Ingredient
*Steak
*Black pepper
*Salt
*Vegetable oil

!How to cook?
*Season each face of the steak with black pepper and salt
*Add small amount of oil to the pan, heat until it boils
*Add steak using tongs, fry each face for at least 2 minutes and 30 seconds. Each face should be a little golden-colored and the edge should be burnt.
*Serve
*Fry each face</pre>
